                "invention-title": [
                    "Method and device for combined cyclic utilization of carbon and hydrogen",
                    "一种用于碳、氢联合循环利用的方法和装置"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to a method and a device for combined cyclic utilization of carbon and hydrogen, which are used for utilizing, converting and storing green hydrogen by adopting a two-step method of a chemical looping principle and solving the problem of intermittency of valley electricity hydrogen production. CO2 reacts with low-valence metal oxide or elemental metal to generate CO, so that high-added-value chemicals are obtained, and meanwhile, the purposes of carbon emission reduction and resource utilization are achieved; the device comprises a renewable power supply, an electrolytic tank anode, an electrolytic tank cathode, an electrolytic tank, a hydrogen storage tank, a reduction reactor, an oxidation reactor, a first throttle valve, a second throttle valve, a third throttle valve, a CO2 storage tank, a direct air carbon capture device, a fourth throttle valve and a Fischer-Tropsch synthesis device. And the targets of carbon emission reduction and resource utilization can be achieved at the same time."
                },
                {
                    "p": "一种用于碳、氢联合循环利用的方法和装置，采用化学链原理的两步法，对绿氢进行利用—转化—存储，解决谷电制氢间歇性的问题。CO2与低价态金属氧化物或单质金属反应生成CO，以获取高附加值化学品，同时达到碳减排与资源化利用目标；其装置包括：可再生电源、电解池阳极、电解池阴极、电解槽、储氢罐、还原反应器、氧化反应器、第一节流阀、第二节流阀、第三节流阀、CO2储存罐、直接空气碳捕集装置、第四节流阀、费托合成装置；可同时达到碳减排与资源化利用目标。"
                }
            ]
